A non -clustred index is stored at one place and table is stored in another place.So this is not physically stored.

Example :
CREATE TABLE EMPLOYEE(
ID INT PRIMARY KEY , // By default create a clusred indes
NAME  VARCHAR(100),
Salary INT
)
//Example
Non-Clustered Index

